high_descs: Look around, then face the box in the room ahead and walk down the hallway; turn left  at the end of hallway; there is a shelf ahead, walk toward the shelf.
Pick up the fork on the left side of the shelf above the bottom shelf.
Turn around to enter the bathroom on your right; walk toward the sink ahead.
Put the fork in the sink, turn on the faucet, soak and rinse the fork in the water; when done, release the water and retrieve the fork.
Turn around and exit the bathroom; turn left then right and walk down the hallway and turn left into living room; keep bearing on your left toward the sidetable ahead.
Put the fork on the front left corner of the sidetable, in front of microwave.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the Fork and place it in front of microwave on the SideTable.

high_descs: Go straight down the hall way, turn left before you reach the bed to the wooden shelf.
Pick up the fork on the second shelf of the wooden rack.
Turn right into the bathroom beside the wooden rack, turn to the sink.
Place the fork in the sink, rinse the fork, pick the fork back up.
Turn right go down the hall, turn left at the end of the hall toward the coffee table, go to the sidetable beside the fridge with the microwave.
Place the fork on the sidetable in front of the microwave in the left front corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean Fork on the SideTable in front of the microwave.
